      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys) with documented V&V procedures; FDA-internal QA protocols applied.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under controlled release management. FDA computational lab maintains documented SQA procedures including version control, regression test suite, and change management. Achieved level meets required level for Medium model risk."
