      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span at least two load levels or environmental conditions representative of COU.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration only. Variation in block material stiffness or offset distance was not explored. This factor is below the required level; the shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given that the ASTM F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard for this device class and additional test conditions are outside the scope of this submission."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
