      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation inputs (geometry, material, BCs) demonstrably match test specimen measurements and test machine configuration.",
      "rationale": "FEA geometry imported from CAD files verified against CMM measurements of tested specimens (max deviation 0.05 mm). Material inputs matched to lot certificates for tested specimens. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry including block separation distance of 100 mm."
